  "detailed_description": "You are a journalist in search of your breakthrough story. A promising lead takes you to the abandoned island of Mythargia where you have to discover its buried history connecting two different dimensions.<br><br><i>Mythargia is a 2D side scrolling retro adventure with emphasis on discovering the island’s story.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the island:</h2>As you search for information you will come face to face with the unnatural present on the island. Find tools and items to help you on your journey further inland. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/9caf4804b4eb32fac740e8f6f9f55e93.poster.avif?t=1754388251\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/9caf4804b4eb32fac740e8f6f9f55e93.webm?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/9caf4804b4eb32fac740e8f6f9f55e93.mp4?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel the secrets:</h2>Leave no stone unturned as you travel deeper into the island. Solve puzzles to find all the clues you can find to get a full picture of what has happened on the island.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/721602f0ed73bb0bfa42762451fde893.poster.avif?t=1754388251\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/721602f0ed73bb0bfa42762451fde893.webm?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/721602f0ed73bb0bfa42762451fde893.mp4?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover the nightmare:</h2>Enter the other dimension and assist the islanders to earn their trust in order to learn more about them and their backgrounds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/a50b53f548765cc11f4ae96eefcffdb0.poster.avif?t=1754388251\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/a50b53f548765cc11f4ae96eefcffdb0.webm?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/a50b53f548765cc11f4ae96eefcffdb0.mp4?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gather information:</h2>Write journal entries and take photos of your journey to understand what has gone down on the island of Mythargia and compile a story of the century.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/7808cf7473ee73cb7368b51fc2d28003.poster.avif?t=1754388251\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/7808cf7473ee73cb7368b51fc2d28003.webm?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2022470/extras/7808cf7473ee73cb7368b51fc2d28003.mp4?t=1754388251\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
